**Fresh Food Hub Operational Protocol:**

```
Weekly Cycle:

Tuesday-Thursday: Order Aggregation
â”œâ”€â”€ Families opt-in to weekly produce box via family_elohim
â”œâ”€â”€ Orders aggregated by neighborhood_elohim (per neighborhood totals)
â”œâ”€â”€ Community_elohim consolidates across 6 neighborhoods
â””â”€â”€ Order sent to farms (Johnson + 2 others): "This week: 73 boxes, breakdown..."

Friday: Farm Preparation
â”œâ”€â”€ Farms harvest and pack produce
â”œâ”€â”€ Coordinate delivery to Priya's community center (Saturday AM)
â””â”€â”€ Community_elohim confirms delivery time, notifies volunteers

Saturday AM: Central Distribution
â”œâ”€â”€ Farms deliver to community center (single drop-off point)
â”œâ”€â”€ Volunteers (James, David, teens) organize by neighborhood
â”œâ”€â”€ Neighborhood coordinators pick up for their networks
â””â”€â”€ Care tokens logged for all volunteer work

Saturday PM: Neighborhood Distribution
â”œâ”€â”€ Families pick up at neighborhood hubs (or home delivery if needed)
â”œâ”€â”€ Sliding scale payment processed (cash, care tokens, subsidized)
â”œâ”€â”€ Families scan QR code to confirm receipt
â””â”€â”€ Feedback collected ("too much kale, want more berries")

